title: got an S on Draft mode but no token?

embed.description: Every game is a story; visit the new League of Legends match history to check out how this one ends and share your own!

body: i just got an s for my performance but i checked my loot and im sure that i dont get another token for my mastery lv7 except the one that i had before. i someone help me pls?

replies.body: Did you get an S- maybe? For M7 tokens you need to get S or S+.
i got an S tho. not S- that's y i need help. ty 4 replying to my post
Not sure then, your best bet would be to submit a support ticket.
